response.original_title: Stardom Triangle Derby I in Korakuen Hall
response.overview: Triangle Derby I is the first annual round-robin six-woman tag team tournament event promoted by World Wonder Ring Stardom.  Singles Match  Rina Amikura vs. Waka Tsukiyama  Tag Team Match  Lady C & Maika vs. Neo Stardom Army (Yuna Mizumori & Yuu)  Triangle Derby I Match  STARS (Hazuki, Koguma & Saya Iida) vs. STARS (Hanan, Mayu Iwatani & Momo Kohgo)  Eight Man Tag Team Match  Queen's Quest (AZM, Miyu Amasaki, Saya Kamitani & Utami Hayashishita) vs. Oedo Tai (Natsuko Tora, Rina, Ruaka & Saki Kashima)  Three Way Nine Man Tag Team Match  Natsupoi, SAKI & Yuko Sakurai vs. Donna del Mondo (Giulia, Mai Sakurai & Thekla) vs. Rebel X Enemy (Maika Ozaki, Maya Yukihi & Ram Kaicho)  Triangle Derby I Match  God's Eye (Ami Sourei, MIRAI & Syuri) vs. Club Venus (Mariah May, Mina Shirakawa & Xia Brookside)
response.title: Stardom Triangle Derby I in Korakuen Hall
